Hi Martina, 

Ok noted, that makes sense. We should be able to work this into some other upgrades we are discussing with Trudy / the SEO agency. I will keep you in the loop, but ideally, we will move it toward the RR model.

full_threads.body:
Hi Heath

I created that page (https://www.metrorehab.com.au/about-us/events/) as a temporary solution when need to urgently promote an event.

As you can see this event has now come and gone so I will delete the contents of this page but leave the page.

We require an events webpage that will automatically hide past events as their date expires. Something similar to what you have created for our Royal Rehab website: https://royalrehab.com.au/news-events/events/ would be ideal.

Thank you very much Heath.
